      "text": "{user}さ～ん\nkana、すっごい大事なお願いがあるんですけど～",
      "startTime": 2.8999999324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんの愛想がいい……）\n（しかも、俺に頼み事だって……？）",
      "startTime": 9.9000000278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "最近、星見プロの子達が何人も\nドラマとか映画に出演してますよね",
      "startTime": 16.8000000278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "それでですね\nkanaも演技の仕事、やってみたいな～って",
      "startTime": 22.4333333611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ほらkana、子供の頃からモデルやってたんで\n何度かドラマにゲストで出たこともありますし",
      "startTime": 30.1666666944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。なら、そっちの人に営業かける時には\nkanaさんのことも売り込んでおきますよ",
      "startTime": 37.6333333611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとですか？　ありがとうございま～～す！！",
      "startTime": 39.8743353326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、つまんない仕事だったら許さないからね\nkanaがモブなんてありえないし",
      "startTime": 47.5666701873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "山田さんほど、ギャラうるさくは言わないけどさ～\nでも、あんま安くても格ってもんがねぇ",
      "startTime": 53.3666701873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は一応、映画の主役やったんでしょ\nなら月ストに勝ったkanaだって主演いけるよね？",
      "startTime": 60.5000035207,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}